{"tid":1920194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【只封BNO？】泰國駐港總領事館：港澳特區護照免簽證入境不受影響","createTime":"2020-03-11T09:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T13:14:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2b1ed582b1fdcda8b1e18a7821a39cfd924af8","tid":1920194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513828-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513828-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0sts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=0e6f38c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513828-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5632109d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513828-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"37e1c7a264834874c592ed912df12bb36fab2809","tid":1920194,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b1ed582b1fdcda8b1e18a7821a39cfd924af8","tid":1920194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513828-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513828-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0sts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=0e6f38c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513828-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5632109d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513828-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"BNO嬴到開巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499b3c5accebad2231e9710534f4974680299ee2","tid":1920194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"泰國駐香港總領事館澄清，香港特區護照持有人免簽證入境泰國的安排不變。<br />\n<br />\n總領事館下午5時許在社交專頁表示，有報道指泰國政府取消一些括免簽證的協議，包括香港特別行政區，泰國駐香港總領使館就此聲明，基於協議乃屬雙邊協議，因此香港及澳門特別行政區護照持有人將不會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n泰國的新型肺炎疫情持續，兩名在曼谷國際機場工作的移民局職員確診。較早時，路透社及泰國傳媒報道，泰國取消香港、南韓及意大利旅客的免簽證入境安排。"},{"pid":"334341a344f70900ff32d82c02dbadb8fe877e2c","tid":1920194,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入"},{"pid":"9e3881ab007f286a617b7524f80a3b363a022ddf","tid":1920194,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"泰駐港總領事館有關免簽證安排不變的貼文已未能找到<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，泰國政府取消一些免簽證協議，包括香港特別行政區，泰國駐香港總領事館下午在社交專頁表示，香港及澳門特別行政區護照持有人免簽證入境泰國的安排不變。不過，晚上已經找不到有關貼文。泰國內政部長較早時宣布，取消香港、南韓及意大利旅客的免簽證入境安排，並暫停向來自中國、印度等18個國家或地區的旅客，發出落地簽證，旅客必須前往泰國大使館申請簽證，並必須向航空公司提供醫生證明，證實自己無感染新型肺炎，才可以登上前往泰國的航班，他們抵達泰國後，亦必須披露強制隔離14日的地點，否則可被罰款2萬泰銖，多次違反檢疫令的人，最高可被判監一年。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-11 20:54:40"},{"pid":"6175ccf10db45bbb2c2166a12ce2f56fc2d16b59","tid":1920194,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"又再彈"}]}